nan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3446 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/15\/ask-love-good-deeds-poor\/","url_meta":{"origin":40463,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Love: I ask you for love of good deeds and the poor","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for good deeds, avoidance of evil deeds, and love for the poor. Forgive me, and have mercy on me. If You intend to put people to trial, take me away\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12005,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/04\/guard-speech-weep-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":40463,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salvation: Guard your speech, weep for your sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what will save us?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRestrain your tongue, let your house be enough for you, and weep for your sins.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2406 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18511,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/al-hajar-al-aswad-sins-bani-adam\/","url_meta":{"origin":40463,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Stone turned black from sins of humankind","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe black stone descended from Paradise and it was whiter than milk, but it became black due to the sins of the children of Adam.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 877 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/05\/intercession-major-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":40463,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sins: We have hope for people of major sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: We withheld ourselves from seeking forgiveness for people of major sins until we heard our Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, say, \u201cVerily, I have delayed my intercession for the people of major sins among my nation for the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \"Thus,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaeli